rebel
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a hostile Maori; an anti-Crown Maori, esp. one captured in Hauhau wars and sent to Dunedin jail
Origin: [none]
Register: historical

Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also adjective/attributive use below
